title: Zena gaming is making an esports team!!!

embed.description: Zena eSports is now looking for OCE Diamond-Plat players who are Jungle/Mid mains looking for a long term team to attend in scrims, tournaments, and scheduled out events, practices, ect.

body: Zena gaming is making an esports team we are currently looking for a plat+ mid and jg if you are interested fill in the forms and we will get back to you if you make the cut good luck :P
